command_block.25.command: sorry for the inconvenience. Minecraft is currently having lag issues due to new particle code. To fix this issue, you can download OptiFine. [click here for website] Download the latest version for 1.13.2, run the executable you download, and restart Minecart, selecting the Optifine setup to start up with. Once downloaded, go to setting -> video settings -> animations and turn of smoke and explosion animations. That should make your game run 800% faster. If you still have issue, just turn off all the animations. Good luck, and game on!

Be careful in this mode. TNT spawns at your feet at an ever increasing pace. Don't stand still!

Sometimes you need more tools. Duel with powerful items spawning across the map.

Survive against hoards of enemies until time runs out. Go solo, outlive your peers, or work with a team to get through the storm. Good luck! Remember:

game.function.game.main.line43: Sorry for the inconvenience. Minecraft is currently having lag issues due to new particle code. To fix this issue, you can download OptiFine. [click here for website] Download the latest version for 1.13.2 (don't download anything else), run the executable you download, and restart Minecart. Select the OptiFine profile on the Minecraft Launcher. Once started, go to settings -> video settings -> animations and turn off smoke and explosion animations. That should make your game run 800% faster. If you still have issues, just turn off all the animations. Good luck, and game on!
